metadata.name: Circular Expressionisms #1
metadata.description:
A 314 Supply Generative Art Collection Made With p5js.

Circles have two options: combine or ignore eachother, they will become larger the more they combine and take the colour of the largest one. The larger they are the more likely they are to ignore eachother.

This collection was created to express interaction between others and groups, more in the Medium!

Prices and supply are inline with pi, 314 and .00314eth respectively, 2 per wallet, 0% royalties.
